title: Anyone Receive The Pumpkin Icon Yet?
body: Just wondering if anyone has received the pumpkin icon for gifting during the teemoing? They should be rolling out right?

replies.body: There are a lot of icons to send out to eligible players, so you'll see some players unlocking them before others.  Our aim is to finish distributing the icons by the 17th, per the [Teemoing ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)page.  Hang tight!
